 365:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *
 366:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *  Function description
 367:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *    Stores a formatted string in SEGGER RTT control block.
 368:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *    This data is read by the host.
 369:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *
 370:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *  Parameters
 371:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *    BufferIndex  Index of "Up"-buffer to be used. (e.g. 0 for "Terminal")
 372:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *    sFormat      Pointer to format string
 373:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *    pParamList   Pointer to the list of arguments for the format string
 374:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccqd67TQ.s 			page 19


 375:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *  Return values
 376:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *    >= 0:  Number of bytes which have been stored in the "Up"-buffer.
 377:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  *     < 0:  Error
 378:ARM_SEGGER_RTT/SEGGER_RTT_printf.c ****  */
